
## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# Dependencies
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
package-lock.json
yarn.lock

# Build outputs
dist/
# build/
release/
*.dmg
*.zip
*.exe
*.AppImage
*.deb
*.rpm
*.snap

# Environment
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store

# Logs
logs/
*.log

# Runtime data
pids/
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# Testing
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# Electron
build/Release/

# Downloaded videos (don't commit user downloads)
Downloads/
*.mp4
*.ts
*.m3u8